{
  "appointmentId": "cole-o-id-do-agendamento-aqui"
}

###

GET {{ApiBabterStyle_HostAddress}}/api/produtos
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{ApiBabterStyle_HostAddress}}/api/produtos/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Accept: application/json

###

